MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2009-2205. Empower Aviation, L.L.C. v. Butler Cty. Bd. of Commrs.

Hamilton App. No. C-090616, 2009-Ohio-6331. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

It is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
